================
playlistfromsong
================


.. image:: https://img.shields.io/pypi/v/playlistfromsong.svg
        :target: https://pypi.python.org/pypi/playlistfromsong

.. image:: https://img.shields.io/travis/schollz/playlistfromsong.svg
